'''Equipment''' in Chrono Trigger includes weapons, armor, helmets, and accessories for all party members.

== Equipment Types ==

=== Weapons ===
Each character has unique weapon types:
* Crono - Katanas
* Marle - Crossbows
* Lucca - Guns
* Robo - Arms
* Frog - Swords (Broadswords)
* Ayla - Fists (cannot equip weapons)
* Magus - Scythes

=== Armor ===
Body protection equipment:
* Available to all characters (gender restrictions on some)
* Provides defense boost
* Some provide elemental resistance

=== Helmets ===
Head protection:
* Defense bonuses
* Status protection on some
* Some class-restricted

=== Accessories ===
Special items providing bonuses:
* Each character can equip one
* Varied effects (stats, protection, abilities)

