== Where to Find Equipment ==

=== Shops ===
Most towns have equipment shops with level-appropriate gear.

=== Chests ===
Dungeons contain stronger equipment in chests.

=== Boss Drops ===
Some bosses drop rare equipment.

=== Crafting ===
* Rainbow Shell items from Melchior
* Prismatic equipment is end-game

=== Black Omen ===
* Can be completed in multiple eras
* Contains best equipment
* Repeatable for farming

